==English==
===Noun===
'''inertia''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#{{physics}} The property of a [[body]] that [[resist]]s any [[change]] to its [[motion]]; equivalent to its [[mass]]
#(''figurative'') In a person, [[unwilling]]ness to take [[action]].

====Synonyms====
*(''unwillingness to take action''): [[idleness]], [[laziness]], [[sloth]], [[slothfulness]]

